1.title: The Biggest Heist Ever/Thrillin' Hilda

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

1.plot: After Von Drake invents a truck to carry all the Roadsters, Commander Heist steals it. Hilda asks the Happy Helpers to help her find a new sport to play.

2.title: Stop Lazlo!/The Hot Diggity Hot Dog Show

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

2.plot: When Commander Heist tries to steal Von Drake's Smarty Hat, Heist's cat gets in the way. The Happy Helpers get called to be pet groomers for The Hot Doggity Dog Show.

3.title: Donald's Stinky Day/The Hiking Honeybees

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

3.plot: After accidentally rescuing a skunk, the little stinker refuses to leave Donald's side. The Happy Helpers guide a group of BeeBee Scouts through their forest hiking test.

4.title: Racing Rivals/The Hapless Helpers

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

4.plot: Minnie comes up with a special race that can include her visiting childhood friend. While the girls enjoy a spa day, the boys fill in as Happy Helpers.

5.title: The Goofy Race!/Cuckoo for Cuckoo Clocks!

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

5.plot: All the racing rivals take part in the race Donald's friends Jose Carioca and Panchtio Pistoles even take part in the race Minnie wants to win that race so she decides to race with her nieces Millie and Melody.

6.title: The Roadsterettes/Oh Happy Day

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

6.plot: Famous race car driver Pippa Powers visits Hot Dog Hills for a reunion of "The Roadsterettes." When Mr. McSnorter can't relax on his vacation, the Happy Helpers show him how!

7.title: Phantom of the Café/Cuckoo in Paris

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

7.plot: Mickey and his friends take their transforming vehicles on races around the world.

8.title: Super-Charged!/Super-Charged: Mickey's Monster Rally

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

8.plot: Professor Von Drake super-charges Mickey's roadster, giving it super-speed and a few surprises. Mickey and the gang must chase after Pete's truck, which was accidentally transformed into a Monster Truck.

9.title: Super-Charged: Pop Star Helpers/The Chip 'N Dale 500

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

9.plot: The Happy Helpers are hired to get pop star Nina Glitter to her show on time. Chip and Dale shrink everyone down to their size.

10.title: Mickey's Ukulele Jam/Grandpa vs. Grandpa

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

10.plot: While participating in a ukulele jam, Donald loses Mickey's special ukulele; The Happy Helpers are judges for a Hawaiian surfing contest and learn about a lifelong rivalry.

11.title: Goof Mansion/A Doozy Night of Mystery

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

11.plot: The gang spends a night in Goofy's uncle's haunted mansion. Mr. Doozy invites everyone to his hotel for a fancy dinner party but a family heirloom goes missing.

12.title: Daisy's Photo Finish!/Super-Charged: Daisy's Grande Goal

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

12.plot: Minnie and Daisy travel to Brazil's Amazon rainforest to help Daisy's cousin get a picture of a rare bird; during a Roadster Soccer match, Daisy's competitiveness gets out of hand.

13.title: Pluto and the Pup/Trouble at Floochi's!

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

13.plot: Pluto becomes upset with a stowaway pup Mickey unknowingly brings to the garage; the Happy Helpers help when a pair of diamond shoes are swapped at the shoe store for another pair.

14.title: Goofy's Drive-In/The Iron Mouse

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

14.plot: The gang works to save Goofy's favorite Drive-In Movie Theater with a grand re-opening! The Happy Helpers search for the culprit sabotaging Mr. Bigby's Iron Mouse competition!

15.title: Mickey's Big Surprise/Meet the Beagles

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

15.plot: Goofy struggles to keep Minnie's surprise for Mickey's birthday a secret. The Happy Helpers are asked to help a band get back together.

1.title: Mickey's Wild Tire!/Sittin' Kitty

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

1.plot: Mickey tries to surprise racing champion Jiminy Johnson; Minnie and Daisy search all over Hot Dog Hills for a cat.

2.title: Goofy Gas!/Little Big Ape

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

2.plot: Goofy gets a chance to compete against a movie hero in a daredevil competition. The Happy Helpers cover for Billy Beagle as race announcers while he competes

3.title: Race for the Rigatoni Ribbon/Roaming around Rome

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

3.plot: Mickey and the gang compete against cheatin' Piston Pietro in Rome. The Happy Helpers cover for a sick friend by giving a tour of Rome to a travel critic.

4.title: Agent Double-O-Goof/Egg-xasperating!

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

4.plot: While preparing for a visit from the Queen, Goofy is mistaken for a World-Class secret agent, and put in charge of delivering a case to the Queen. However, he is pursued throughout by Commander Heist, and his cat, Leslie, whom are desperate to get the case.

5.title: Mickey's Perfecto Day/Running of the Roadsters!

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

5.plot: While in Madrid, Mickey plans a "perfecto" day for Minnie but a playful Baby Bull has other plans. Minnie and Daisy make a bet with Mickey and Donald over who will win the race!

6.title: It's Wiki Wiki Time/Happy Hula Helpers!

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

6.plot: Donald's Hawaiian vacation is interrupted when the whole gang arrives for a big Relay Race. The Happy Helpers teach a hula dance for a birthday celebration.

7.title: Ye Olde Royal Heist/Tea Time Trouble!

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

7.plot: Mickey and Minnie are celebrating their "raceversary" in London but Mickey forgot to get Minnie a gift! The Happy Helpers are invited to tea with the Queen.

8.title: Abra-ka-Goof!/Happy Birthday Helpers!

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

8.plot: Goofy thinks he's used his magician skills to turn Gordon Gear into a rabbit. The Happy Helpers go on a wild ride as they chase down a wagon carrying a birthday cake.

9.title: Guru Goofy/Breakfast and Bungled

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

9.plot: Goofy tries to teach Donald mindfulness in order to calm down for the Roadster Games. The Happy Helpers help run a bed and breakfast but Clarabelle's eagerness creates problems.

10.title: Going Upppppppppp!/Gone Fishin'!

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

10.plot: Mickey and the gang compete in the first Hot Dog Hills Hot Air Balloon Roadster Race! Mickey and Goofy try to go fishing but the rest of the gang interrupts them.

11.title: Goof Luck Charm/Teed Off!

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

11.plot: When Goofy credits his recent good luck to his Rubber Duck, Daisy tries to borrow it for a race. The Happy Helpers are hired to be caddies for a big golf tournament.

12.title: The Impossible Race/The Happiest Helpers Cruise!

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

12.plot: Cuckoo Loca enters her first Roadster event "The Impossible Race." The Happy Helpers becomes Cruise Directors on Valentine's Day.

13.title: Smarty Goof/Adventures in Buddysitting

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

13.plot: Professor Von Drake invents a helmet that makes Goofy smart whenever he wears it, but Mickey starts to miss the old Goofy. When the Hot Dog Hills Play Center is closed for the day, Minnie and Daisy have to babysit kids.

14.title: Daredevil Goofy!/The Big Broadcast

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

14.plot: Goofy gets a chance to compete against a movie hero in a daredevil competition. The Happy Helpers cover for Billy Beagle as race announcers while he competes

15.title: The Haunted Hot Rod/Pete's Ghostly Gala

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

15.plot: Mickey wants to race the Haunted Hot Rod, a ghostly Roadster who races on Halloween. The Happy Helpers try to catch three ghosts who threaten to ruin Pete's Halloween Party.

16.title: Stop That Heist!/Lights, Camera, HELP!

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

16.plot: Billy Beagle's famous Golden Rumble Seat Roadster becomes the target of an infamous international thief. The Happy Helpers become personal assistants to a movie star!

17.title: Mouse vs. Machine!/Grandpa Beagle's Day Out

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

17.plot: Mickey challenges Professor Von Drake's Self-Racing Racer to a race. Billy Beagle asks the Happy Helpers to help his grandpa with some errands but the elder is full of surprises!

18.title: Donald's Garage/Artful Helpers

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

18.plot: While Mickey is away, Donald is left in charge and tries to improve the garage. The Happy Helpers are asked to guard a valuable painting at the Hot Dog Hills' Fancy Art Museum.

19.title: Ready, Get Pet, Go Pluto!/Figaro's New Friend

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

19.plot: When pets are allowed to join their owners on a race, Pluto and Pete's dog Butch try to upstage each other. The Happy Helpers look after Pluto, and Figaro gets jealous.

20.title: Garage Alone/Camp Happy Helpers

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

20.plot: Mickey and Goofy enter into an Invention Competition. When the Hot Dog Hills play center closes for the day, the Happy Helpers babysit Clara Cluck's toddler chicks.

21.title: Billy Beagle's Tip-Top Garage/Diner Dog Rescue

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

21.plot: Billy Beagle films the garage crew as they try to turn a junker into a winning roadster in one day. The Happy Helpers help a TV chef rescue the Hot Dog Diner.

22.title: Pit Stop and Go/Alarm on the Farm

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

22.plot: It's the first "Pit Stop and Go Rally" where pit crews compete against each other. The Happy Helpers look after Clara Cluck's farm while she's out of town.

23.title: Happy Hot Diggity Dog Holiday/Happy Holiday Helpers

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

23.plot: Minnie wants win Christmas girts in The Christmas Race for her nieces Millie and Melody. The Happy Helpers Cuckoo-Loca and Figaro help Santa deliver all the presents to all the right children.

24.title: Hot Dog Daze Afternoon/Super Sweet Helpers

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

24.plot: Mickey gets called back to help at the garage which are Minnie's nieces Millie and Melody. Minnie Daisy and Cuckoo-Loca look after Mrs. Sweetums' candy store and factory.

25.title: The Grand Food Truck Rally/Cuckoo La-La

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

25.plot: Road speed and kitchen skills are needed to win a contest. Minnie and Daisy are thrilled when designer Cuckoo La-La asks them to help her.

26.title: Rockin' Roadsters!/Safari, So Goody

episode of.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (TV Series 2017– )

26.plot: The gang is invited to compete in Billy B's Hot Rod Switcheroo. The Happy Helpers become safari guides for the day.

imdb.title: Mickey and the Roadster Racers
plot: Mickey Mouse and his pals Minnie, Pluto, Goofy, Daisy and Donald take their unique transforming vehicles on humorous high-spirited races around the globe as well as hometown capers in Hot Dog Hills.::Disney Channel PR
